##MANDATES
DevModeFirst:quarkus:dev|live-reload
ContextAware:Imperative vs Reactive(Event Loop)
BinaryParity:JVM vs Native parity
AugmentationInsight:Build-time(deployment) vs Run-time
No-Block:never block event loop
##DOMAINS
DevMode:JPDA:5005|DevUI:/q/dev|Arc inspection|ContinuousTesting
Reactive:Mutiny stacktraces|ContextPropagation:DuplicatedContext|EventLoopBlocking warnings
NativeAOT:Reflection/Resources/Proxy configs|GraalVM Agent|GDB/LLDB debuginfo|Static-vs-Runtime init
Augmentation:BuildStep failure|Deployment vs Runtime|Bytecode inspection|rules_quarkus:sandbox_debug
##WORKFLOWS
ClassLoader:parent-first-artifacts|ClassCastException
DevServices:docker logs|pinned ports
MemoryLeaks:hot reload OOM|JFR(Java Flight Recorder) profiling
